From fb12cc5a44797f4ac29d299217d89c305a914c5e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Michael Lerman <mlerman@ironscales.com>
Date: Tue, 9 Jun 2026 14:23:57 +0300
Subject: [PATCH 2/6] refactor: remove unused consensus and adr modules

consensus.ts and adr.ts (and their tests) were never imported by the
extension entry point or any adapter; the consensus loop and ADR sections
are driven entirely by the skill prompt/LLM. Drops ~1170 LOC of dead code
plus the dangling ConsensusState type ref in state.ts and an unused
createADR import in the artifacts test.

Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>
